WEBVTT

01:34.840 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:38.840
NANWU UNIVERSITY

01:38.920 --> 01:39.920
Is that Sang Yan?

01:40.000 --> 01:40.880
Hurry up.

01:40.960 --> 01:41.800
Let's go check it out.

01:43.240 --> 01:44.480
He's so handsome.

01:44.560 --> 01:45.600
He's so fair.

01:45.680 --> 01:47.640
- Exactly.
- He's so tall. I want his WeChat.

01:47.720 --> 01:48.720
Let's go check it out.

01:48.800 --> 01:49.640
Sang Yan!

01:51.280 --> 01:53.280
He heard us! Didn't he hear us?

01:53.360 --> 01:55.240
Quiet down. He can hear everything.

01:55.880 --> 01:57.720
- What's going on?
- They said I'm good-looking,

01:57.800 --> 01:59.120
and they want to add me on WeChat.

01:59.200 --> 02:00.440
Isn't that pretty common?

02:02.000 --> 02:03.240
Well, to you, I guess it's true.

02:04.600 --> 02:06.840
The National Day holiday is approaching.
What's your plan?

02:08.440 --> 02:10.320
I have no plan. How about you?

02:10.960 --> 02:12.200
I'm going back to Yihe.

02:12.280 --> 02:13.800
Why don't you come with me?

02:13.880 --> 02:15.280
You seem interested in my hometown.

02:18.480 --> 02:21.200
- Let's talk later.
- "Let's talk later."

02:21.280 --> 02:23.400
You sound like I'm begging you.
If you don't want to, forget it.

02:24.760 --> 02:25.760
Are we still eating or not?

02:32.240 --> 02:34.960
YIHE UNIVERSITY

02:43.120 --> 02:44.040
Jiang.

02:45.600 --> 02:46.640
Jiang.

02:51.400 --> 02:53.160
I've been waiting here for half a day.

02:54.760 --> 02:55.680
Did you see me for something?

02:56.680 --> 02:58.960
Can't I just come to check on you?

03:00.600 --> 03:02.760
By the way,
I brought you some chili sauce.

03:02.840 --> 03:04.480
It's the kind you loved
when you were a kid.

03:04.560 --> 03:06.160
I also brought you some local specialties.

03:06.720 --> 03:08.080
I've quit eating
spicy food for a long time.

03:09.240 --> 03:11.400
That's okay.
You can give it to your dorm mates.

03:11.480 --> 03:12.600
They'll definitely like it.

03:12.680 --> 03:13.520
Here you go.

03:21.440 --> 03:23.920
- Thank you.
- No need to be polite.

03:25.320 --> 03:26.160
I'm leaving now.

03:26.800 --> 03:28.200
Wait…

03:30.760 --> 03:31.600
Mom!

03:32.720 --> 03:34.920
Take it quickly. Take it.

03:35.000 --> 03:36.880
We're still going
to the pedestrian street. Hurry up.

03:36.960 --> 03:39.640
Okay, I'll be done in a second.

03:39.720 --> 03:40.720
Why didn't you greet your sister?

03:43.760 --> 03:44.600
Hello.

03:45.160 --> 03:47.000
What's good to eat or do in Yihe?

03:47.080 --> 03:49.080
- Can you recommend something?
- I'm not very familiar.

03:49.160 --> 03:51.240
You're attending Yihe University.
How can you not be familiar?

03:51.320 --> 03:54.160
Alright, let's finish up. Go rest now.

04:04.280 --> 04:05.120
Let's go, Mom.

04:21.680 --> 04:22.760
3,355 DAYS

04:23.440 --> 04:25.680
- Smile!
- Look at her little hands!

04:25.760 --> 04:26.840
You see.

04:28.360 --> 04:29.360
Good girl.

04:31.440 --> 04:32.280
Who is it?

04:32.360 --> 04:34.360
DAY 293 OF LIVING TOGETHER

04:34.440 --> 04:36.200
They're so small.

04:36.280 --> 04:37.880
Look at her little hands.

04:37.960 --> 04:39.960
Su Tian, may I hug?

04:40.040 --> 04:40.960
How can you hug her?

04:41.040 --> 04:42.080
Only I can.

04:44.920 --> 04:46.200
I didn't mean to hug Su Tian.

04:46.280 --> 04:47.600
I meant I want to hug the baby.

04:47.680 --> 04:49.160
- That's not okay either.
- Let me hug her…

04:49.760 --> 04:51.680
Did you wash your hands?
You have to wash your hands first.

04:51.760 --> 04:54.160
I washed them.
I even sanitized them with alcohol.

04:54.240 --> 04:55.840
- Take her out.
- Let me take you out.

04:55.920 --> 04:57.040
Take care.

04:59.560 --> 05:00.960
Do it gently.

05:01.720 --> 05:03.040
Take your time.

05:03.120 --> 05:04.600
Right.

05:09.760 --> 05:10.880
Let me hug her.

05:14.760 --> 05:16.760
There are still 56 days left.

05:23.400 --> 05:24.560
How come you're out?

05:24.640 --> 05:25.760
Just checking on you.

05:25.840 --> 05:27.480
How's it going? Tell me quickly.

05:28.920 --> 05:29.760
Well,

05:30.600 --> 05:31.760
I'm still working on it.

05:31.840 --> 05:33.560
No progress at all?

05:33.640 --> 05:34.960
Is he keeping you hanging?

05:35.040 --> 05:36.120
No.

05:36.200 --> 05:37.600
He probably doesn't know I'm pursuing him.

05:38.600 --> 05:41.400
So, your relationship
hasn't progressed at all?

05:42.760 --> 05:43.800
I'm not really sure.

05:43.880 --> 05:46.360
Didn't you do anything at all?

05:47.280 --> 05:48.560
Not exactly.

05:50.000 --> 05:52.160
It's just that I don't know
where to start.

05:52.760 --> 05:54.760
You could start with his hobbies.

05:55.400 --> 05:56.720
Hobbies?

06:02.680 --> 06:04.040
Do you know how to play?

06:04.800 --> 06:07.120
Use your skills!
What does a basic attack mean?

06:07.200 --> 06:08.440
Can you focus on your fire?

06:12.640 --> 06:14.280
What's up? Did the other side
pay you to play like this?

06:14.360 --> 06:15.200
Why are you playing like that?

06:21.400 --> 06:24.000
- What's wrong?
- Nothing.

06:30.480 --> 06:33.200
You seem like a different person
when you're playing games.

06:38.520 --> 06:40.960
Keep playing. I'll take a break.

06:47.960 --> 06:51.080
E-sports sometimes involve
some verbal sparring.

06:51.160 --> 06:52.000
It's…

06:52.840 --> 06:53.880
It's totally normal.

06:56.880 --> 06:58.360
NANWU TV STATION

06:58.440 --> 06:59.480
What a kid!

06:59.560 --> 07:01.600
He'd skip meals just to play games.

07:01.680 --> 07:04.480
He's been playing
this game a lot recently.

07:05.760 --> 07:07.880
- How's it?
- It's pretty fun.

07:07.960 --> 07:09.920
I used to play it in college.

07:10.000 --> 07:11.000
But I haven't played in a long time.

07:11.680 --> 07:13.520
It feels a bit rusty now.

07:14.360 --> 07:15.240
You're playing it yourself?

07:17.440 --> 07:18.880
You can play with him!

07:18.960 --> 07:20.760
What's the point of playing by yourself?

07:21.440 --> 07:22.640
I'm too bad at it.

07:22.720 --> 07:24.520
I'm afraid he'll criticize me.

07:24.600 --> 07:25.760
No way.

07:25.840 --> 07:27.680
When you play games with boys,

07:27.760 --> 07:30.440
they just feel superior,
like they're helping a girl out.

07:30.520 --> 07:32.840
So, no matter how bad you play,

07:32.920 --> 07:34.160
they won't criticize you.

07:34.760 --> 07:37.320
No. He won't treat me
any differently just because it's me.

07:38.440 --> 07:39.280
Hello.

07:39.960 --> 07:40.800
Hello.

07:41.680 --> 07:44.240
Yifan, you play this game too?

07:45.320 --> 07:47.920
This game is slow to level up
if no one's helping.

07:48.000 --> 07:48.840
Want me to help you level up?

07:48.920 --> 07:50.200
No need. I'm not in a hurry.

07:51.480 --> 07:54.480
Mobile games are boring to play alone.

07:57.840 --> 07:59.640
ADD FRIEND: MR. MU

07:59.720 --> 08:00.840
Done.

08:00.920 --> 08:02.680
I'm online all night.

08:02.760 --> 08:05.280
If you need help, Yifan,
just call me anytime.

08:09.760 --> 08:10.960
Have you had lunch?

08:11.880 --> 08:13.760
Yeah. I just finished.

08:15.240 --> 08:16.840
Have you sorted the files?

08:20.920 --> 08:22.480
Looks like…

08:23.000 --> 08:24.080
not yet.

08:31.920 --> 08:32.799
Okay.

08:32.880 --> 08:34.400
- Thank you.
- Thanks for your hard work.

08:42.880 --> 08:45.120
Sang Yan. Where are you going?

08:45.800 --> 08:47.480
Where else would I go?
Going home after work.

08:47.560 --> 08:49.000
Going home?

08:49.080 --> 08:50.480
Did you forget that you promised

08:50.560 --> 08:51.640
to join me at Overtime tonight?

08:53.720 --> 08:54.560
Do we have to do it today?

08:54.640 --> 08:56.400
Of course, it has to be today.
Today's the shareholders' meeting.

08:56.480 --> 08:58.560
I've already made plans
with Qian Fei and Chen Junwen.

08:58.640 --> 09:00.080
They're just waiting for us. Let's go.

09:02.240 --> 09:03.840
Come on. Let's go!

09:04.640 --> 09:07.400
The drinks and dishes are here!

09:08.720 --> 09:10.600
The dishes, drinks, and Sang Yan are here!

09:10.680 --> 09:11.840
You're here.

09:13.520 --> 09:15.000
What a rare guest,

09:15.080 --> 09:16.160
Mr. Sang.

09:16.240 --> 09:18.840
Mr. Qian has been giving me
a hard time recently.

09:18.920 --> 09:21.400
It's definitely not that serious.

09:21.480 --> 09:23.560
It's just that recently, the shareholders

09:23.640 --> 09:25.960
can't get a grasp on your movements.

09:26.040 --> 09:27.840
- Tell us about it.
- Seriously?

09:27.920 --> 09:28.960
Seriously, tell us.

09:29.040 --> 09:30.360
If I really tell you,
I'm afraid you'll feel off.

09:30.440 --> 09:32.360
You might get so jealous
that you'd lose your cool.

09:32.440 --> 09:33.360
You could even get really mad.

09:33.440 --> 09:35.760
Hey, what does he mean by that?

09:35.840 --> 09:38.080
He said there's a girl
chasing him recently.

09:38.160 --> 09:39.720
He doesn't have time for us.

09:39.800 --> 09:40.840
What's the big deal?

09:40.920 --> 09:41.840
Are you crazy?

09:41.920 --> 09:43.520
It's not like this is the first time
someone's chasing you.

09:43.600 --> 09:45.520
We've never seen him
show off like this before.

09:45.600 --> 09:46.560
Right?

09:47.320 --> 09:49.160
You like her too, don't you?

09:50.320 --> 09:52.440
Yes. So what?

09:52.520 --> 09:54.880
Really? Who?

09:55.640 --> 09:57.000
Let me figure this out.

09:57.080 --> 09:58.640
You like her too,

09:58.720 --> 10:00.760
but you're waiting for her
to come chase you?

10:00.840 --> 10:02.000
That's kind of passive.

10:02.080 --> 10:05.120
You're a man.
You can't just keep her hanging.

10:06.200 --> 10:07.040
Qian Fei,

10:08.000 --> 10:09.520
do I need you to teach me?

10:09.600 --> 10:11.960
If you had even a fraction
of my emotional intelligence,

10:12.040 --> 10:13.360
you wouldn't be playing backup in college.

10:13.440 --> 10:14.760
Stop!

10:15.280 --> 10:16.760
I'll take the punishment.

10:16.840 --> 10:21.800
Honestly, Sang Yan.
You always rub salt in others' wounds.

10:21.880 --> 10:23.760
And this is from ages ago.

10:23.840 --> 10:26.160
Every time there's a gathering,
you bring it up.

10:26.920 --> 10:28.760
Is it that new intern from our company?

10:28.840 --> 10:29.840
She's probably a junior or senior.

10:29.920 --> 10:31.000
She's quite pretty.

10:31.080 --> 10:33.320
Wow, you, an old dog chasing a young pup.

10:33.400 --> 10:34.640
She's still in college.

10:35.600 --> 10:36.720
I got it.

10:36.800 --> 10:37.880
He likes younger girls.

10:37.960 --> 10:39.360
- Get lost.
- Pfft.

10:39.440 --> 10:43.520
Love has nothing to do with age.
Right, Jun?

10:43.600 --> 10:45.080
You two together,

10:45.160 --> 10:48.000
even if she's five to ten years younger,
it doesn't matter.

10:48.520 --> 10:50.560
Looks like it's not that intern.

10:50.640 --> 10:53.760
Is it the girl
who joined the company with you?

10:53.840 --> 10:54.880
Wrong again?

10:56.200 --> 10:57.480
What are your plans with that girl?

10:57.560 --> 10:58.680
What plans?

10:59.400 --> 11:01.480
She wants to chase me. What can I do?

11:02.040 --> 11:03.560
- Just wait to be chased.
- So shameless.

11:03.640 --> 11:05.640
Too arrogant.

11:06.480 --> 11:08.080
Why are you talking about me all the time?

11:08.160 --> 11:09.360
Doesn't he have things going on?

11:11.200 --> 11:12.320
Oh, you little brat
have things going on too?

11:13.440 --> 11:14.680
No, it's just…

11:14.760 --> 11:16.080
Su Haoan.

11:20.440 --> 11:21.880
You are gathering?

11:21.960 --> 11:22.920
Is it inconvenient for me to come?

11:23.000 --> 11:25.360
No, it's fine.

11:26.320 --> 11:27.880
It's fine, whatever.

11:31.440 --> 11:32.520
Who is it?

11:42.440 --> 11:43.680
What are you laughing at?

11:46.360 --> 11:47.400
Nothing.

11:47.960 --> 11:49.760
I'm just really happy you're here.

11:57.360 --> 11:58.560
Has she been here before?

12:02.040 --> 12:03.040
How's Grandpa been recently?

12:05.720 --> 12:06.680
He's good.

12:07.280 --> 12:08.360
By the way,

12:08.440 --> 12:09.680
I might have to move back home soon.

12:10.360 --> 12:12.400
If you move back,
Grandpa will be so happy.

12:13.440 --> 12:14.760
Just don't find me annoying.

12:16.400 --> 12:18.200
Have you told Grandpa

12:18.280 --> 12:19.880
that you know about his condition?

12:22.560 --> 12:24.720
I'll wait a few more days.

12:24.800 --> 12:26.000
After all, Woodie just passed away.

12:26.080 --> 12:28.000
I don't want to upset him right now.

12:28.080 --> 12:29.840
How is this upsetting him?

12:29.920 --> 12:31.400
It's just caring for him.

12:35.560 --> 12:39.200
Fine. I don't have the right
to tell you what to do.

12:40.640 --> 12:42.280
You can tell me what to do.

12:42.800 --> 12:45.400
How are you so funny? You even want that?

12:45.480 --> 12:47.880
No wonder your ex-girlfriends
had you wrapped around their fingers.

12:49.000 --> 12:51.160
No. What I mean is,

12:51.960 --> 12:54.440
you've helped me a lot with this.

12:54.520 --> 12:56.840
Your advice has been really useful.

12:56.920 --> 12:57.800
And

12:58.640 --> 13:00.000
you've never asked for anything in return.

13:01.160 --> 13:02.280
How can I be that kind of person?

13:02.360 --> 13:03.800
Exactly because you're not like that,

13:03.880 --> 13:05.720
I'm even more touched.

13:06.920 --> 13:08.080
And

13:10.080 --> 13:13.200
I can feel your sincerity.

13:15.080 --> 13:16.720
What are you babbling on about?

13:16.800 --> 13:19.040
You almost made me forget why I came.

13:19.640 --> 13:20.480
Just forget it then.

13:22.720 --> 13:23.840
How about I go visit Grandpa tomorrow?

13:24.520 --> 13:25.840
Sure. What's wrong?

13:27.560 --> 13:28.640
I found Woodie.

13:36.720 --> 13:38.480
INVITING YOU TO JOIN MR. MU'S TEAM
DECLINED

13:41.880 --> 13:46.200
YIFAN, PLEASE ACCEPT MY INVITATION

13:49.800 --> 13:52.920
MR. MU: YIFAN, PLEASE ACCEPT
MY INVITATION, I'LL HELP YOU

13:57.040 --> 14:01.080
WARM WATER
I'M ABOUT TO LOG OFF, MAYBE NEXT TIME

14:09.760 --> 14:11.200
ZHAO YUANDONG

14:27.960 --> 14:29.000
Hello.

14:29.080 --> 14:31.600
Jiang. Are you asleep?

14:34.360 --> 14:35.280
Not yet.

14:37.000 --> 14:38.600
I just miss you.

14:39.280 --> 14:40.360
And I want to hear your voice.

14:41.040 --> 14:42.760
I'm fine. Don't worry.

14:43.280 --> 14:45.640
The last few times we met, I upset you.

14:46.840 --> 14:48.040
It's all my fault.

14:49.600 --> 14:50.880
During the Spring Festival,

14:52.040 --> 14:53.680
I didn't think it through.
I should have known

14:53.760 --> 14:55.560
that you don't like visiting my place.

14:56.160 --> 14:57.960
I had you live here once,

14:58.040 --> 15:00.200
then I had to make
you leave shortly after.

15:00.920 --> 15:02.360
It was really unavoidable.

15:05.000 --> 15:07.200
How about this? Tell me your address,

15:07.280 --> 15:08.720
and I'll come over
to cook something nice for you.

15:10.400 --> 15:12.160
When I said I wouldn't go
to your place anymore,

15:12.240 --> 15:13.160
do you think it was

15:13.240 --> 15:15.000
because I couldn't fit
into your current family?

15:16.720 --> 15:17.560
Then…

15:18.480 --> 15:20.320
was it because of your aunt?

15:22.360 --> 15:24.080
Let's leave it at that.
I have to get up early tomorrow.

16:46.840 --> 16:48.160
What a bully you are!

16:49.560 --> 16:50.920
You've taken up both beds.

17:52.680 --> 17:55.920
Wen Shuangjiang, can you chase me

17:56.600 --> 17:57.760
a little more obviously?

18:00.280 --> 18:01.840
Otherwise, I won't feel certain.

18:06.600 --> 18:08.480
If you're not willing
to extend a hand first,

18:10.720 --> 18:12.280
how would I dare…

18:16.600 --> 18:18.160
to give myself to you again?

19:20.960 --> 19:22.120
Where did Sang Yan sleep last night?

19:23.880 --> 19:26.440
I hope it's not like before.

19:29.080 --> 19:30.560
Didn't he come back yesterday?

20:05.960 --> 20:07.160
You…

20:08.560 --> 20:10.320
I… I…

20:10.400 --> 20:13.080
Last night when I was sleepwalking,
did you come back?

20:15.080 --> 20:16.960
So, you were pushed out and slept here?

20:19.400 --> 20:21.960
You should've woken me up
and kicked me out.

20:22.040 --> 20:23.840
If you locked the door,
I definitely wouldn't have gotten in.

20:23.920 --> 20:24.960
You'd pick the lock.

20:25.040 --> 20:26.920
I don't have that skill.

20:27.000 --> 20:28.040
You do.

20:29.360 --> 20:31.920
For the sake of invading me,
what wouldn't you do?

20:35.080 --> 20:37.520
So, if I really invaded you,
you'd lock the door, right?

20:45.160 --> 20:46.400
Then, come on.

21:00.040 --> 21:02.440
Now… do you understand?

21:05.080 --> 21:07.320
If you don't lock the door,
it will be like this.

21:17.160 --> 21:18.280
What's going on?

21:33.760 --> 21:34.880
Nothing happened, right?

22:02.040 --> 22:03.120
Now you dare?

22:07.600 --> 22:08.640
I don't.

22:10.800 --> 22:11.920
Next time.

22:12.000 --> 22:13.280
I have to go to work now.

22:38.680 --> 22:39.600
Now you dare?

22:44.400 --> 22:46.200
Should I be braver?

22:57.400 --> 22:58.640
Alright. Grandpa.

22:58.720 --> 23:00.560
I've set reminders on your phone.

23:00.640 --> 23:01.640
Take this medicine.

23:01.720 --> 23:03.640
One dose a day,
split into morning, noon, and night.

23:03.720 --> 23:06.000
Keep the medicine with you.
When the phone rings, take a pill.

23:06.080 --> 23:07.120
Enough.

23:07.200 --> 23:08.760
What's up?

23:08.840 --> 23:11.120
Do you think I'm too old to do anything?

23:11.200 --> 23:13.520
You're here to bother me?

23:13.600 --> 23:16.240
With all this free time,
go find yourself a girlfriend.

23:18.440 --> 23:19.960
Uncle Ma, is Grandpa here?

23:20.040 --> 23:21.960
I came to check on him.

23:22.040 --> 23:23.240
Let's eat together.

23:27.120 --> 23:28.920
Is this the visit
you were talking about yesterday?

23:30.880 --> 23:33.480
- How's Grandpa's mood today?
- Terrible.

23:34.880 --> 23:36.080
Then it's all over.

23:36.160 --> 23:38.360
Will the gift I bring
make him even unhappier?

23:38.440 --> 23:40.160
When did you become so timid?

23:41.480 --> 23:42.840
Who said I'm timid?

23:43.480 --> 23:44.800
Woodie, come here!

23:47.640 --> 23:49.360
Good dog. Come here.

23:49.440 --> 23:51.320
Good dog.

23:51.400 --> 23:52.440
Come here.

23:53.400 --> 23:54.440
Over here.

23:54.520 --> 23:57.800
I found it at the animal shelter.

23:57.880 --> 24:00.160
It's only one year old.
Could you adopt it?

24:00.240 --> 24:01.760
Its name is really Woodie.

24:01.840 --> 24:04.200
I shouted this name
among all the dogs, "Woodie!"

24:04.280 --> 24:05.120
Only it turned around.

24:05.200 --> 24:06.880
It was jumping around, trying to kiss me.

24:06.960 --> 24:09.080
Trying to kiss you? Is it that nice?

24:11.680 --> 24:12.520
But Grandpa,

24:12.600 --> 24:14.880
It's not completely black.
It's only half black.

24:14.960 --> 24:15.960
You won't be mad, right?

24:16.560 --> 24:19.560
No. Woodie.

24:20.960 --> 24:21.800
Don't tie it up.

24:24.360 --> 24:25.440
Woodie.

24:28.720 --> 24:30.640
Don't bite randomly!
The furniture is expensive!

24:30.720 --> 24:32.480
Come here! Over here, Woodie!

24:34.600 --> 24:35.520
Grandpa,

24:36.240 --> 24:37.960
she's a great girl.

24:39.960 --> 24:41.760
But you're terrible.

24:42.800 --> 24:44.920
Now the best has appeared.

24:45.000 --> 24:47.680
It's up to you to seize this opportunity.

24:49.480 --> 24:51.680
Woodie! Come here!

24:51.760 --> 24:55.360
Good dog. Let's shake hands.
Come on. That hand.

24:55.440 --> 24:57.240
Come on. This one. That one.

24:57.320 --> 24:59.320
Good. Good, Woodie.

24:59.400 --> 25:00.440
Good.

25:04.840 --> 25:08.040
43 DAYS REMAINING

25:08.120 --> 25:10.080
42 DAYS REMAINING

25:10.160 --> 25:12.800
41 DAYS REMAINING

25:12.880 --> 25:15.240
40 DAYS REMAINING
39 DAYS REMAINING

25:15.320 --> 25:19.480
38, 37… 22 DAYS REMAINING

25:19.560 --> 25:21.760
21 DAYS REMAINING
20 DAYS REMAINING

25:21.840 --> 25:23.480
19 DAYS REMAINING

25:23.560 --> 25:25.240
18 DAYS REMAINING

25:25.320 --> 25:27.160
17 DAYS REMAINING

25:27.240 --> 25:29.200
16 DAYS REMAINING

25:29.280 --> 25:32.440
15 DAYS REMAINING

25:55.720 --> 25:57.920
CORAL JADE ROBE
BASE ATTRIBUTES, SMELTING EFFECT

26:10.040 --> 26:12.040
JOURNALISM PSYCHOLOGY

26:24.680 --> 26:26.520
Recently, I've been playing this game too.

26:29.640 --> 26:31.160
Really?

26:31.240 --> 26:32.160
When?

26:33.640 --> 26:35.280
Just recently.

26:35.360 --> 26:36.680
It's pretty fun.

26:36.760 --> 26:39.600
Perfect. I got new gear.
Want to join me in a round?

26:40.200 --> 26:41.080
Sure.

26:41.960 --> 26:43.680
What rank are you at?

26:44.400 --> 26:45.920
Almost at the top rank.

26:46.000 --> 26:47.280
So strong.

26:49.000 --> 26:49.920
Let's go.

26:50.840 --> 26:51.840
Next time.

26:52.640 --> 26:54.120
I've got some work to do.

27:04.480 --> 27:07.440
By the way, are you available this Friday?

27:08.480 --> 27:10.440
- What's up?
- Well,

27:11.920 --> 27:13.200
I heard from a colleague

27:13.280 --> 27:16.000
that there's a really good restaurant
near your company.

27:16.080 --> 27:18.800
If you have time,
maybe we can go eat together.

27:35.240 --> 27:37.400
Finally, you're paying back
the meal you owed me, huh?

27:40.280 --> 27:41.280
So, are you free?

27:45.600 --> 27:47.320
Then I'll come to your office building

27:47.400 --> 27:48.960
on Friday.

27:51.320 --> 27:55.360
Because I might finish
work early on Friday.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.480
So, I can come find you.

27:56.560 --> 27:57.600
If it's inconvenient,

27:57.680 --> 27:59.160
we can just meet at the restaurant.

28:00.040 --> 28:02.000
No need. I'll be coming back that day.

28:03.160 --> 28:04.520
We can go together then.

28:21.640 --> 28:22.960
I'll remind you again

28:23.040 --> 28:24.160
this Friday.

28:35.240 --> 28:36.640
What are your plans for the weekend?

28:36.720 --> 28:39.520
I have two tickets for Mao Buyi's concert.

28:40.280 --> 28:42.440
I'm just going to relax
at home this weekend.

28:43.240 --> 28:45.800
What? You're still young.

28:46.760 --> 28:48.200
That's why I need to chill.

28:48.280 --> 28:50.400
Yifan, hello!

28:50.480 --> 28:51.720
Whose concert do you like?

28:51.800 --> 28:53.080
I'll try to grab more tickets.

29:41.920 --> 29:44.560
- Have you been waiting a long time?
- No.

29:46.480 --> 29:47.360
Let's go.

29:53.880 --> 29:54.760
By the way,

29:55.480 --> 29:57.200
didn't you come back because of something?

30:05.080 --> 30:06.040
What's wrong?

30:07.640 --> 30:09.400
It's because the air
smells really good here.

30:16.800 --> 30:18.320
Let me help you with the navigation.

30:18.400 --> 30:19.400
Okay.

30:21.920 --> 30:23.960
We're going to Spring Garden.

30:26.080 --> 30:27.600
Spring Garden?

30:30.560 --> 30:32.040
What's wrong? You don't like it?

30:33.080 --> 30:35.120
- No.
- I can pick another place.

30:36.040 --> 30:37.040
No need.

30:38.720 --> 30:40.440
- Do you have any food restrictions?
- Quite a few.

30:40.520 --> 30:41.880
- Hot pot?
- Too hot.

30:41.960 --> 30:43.440
- Barbecue?
- Too smelly.

30:43.520 --> 30:45.040
- Sichuan food?
- Too spicy.

30:46.960 --> 30:48.480
I asked you out for dinner before,

30:48.560 --> 30:50.280
and you didn't like
the dishes I suggested.

30:50.360 --> 30:51.200
It's really hard.

30:51.880 --> 30:52.880
I just didn't like them back then.

30:54.120 --> 30:55.440
Just didn't like them back then…

30:56.640 --> 30:59.240
So now, you do?

31:07.280 --> 31:08.320
Isn't it noisy outside?

31:09.080 --> 31:10.920
The breeze feels so nice.

31:22.920 --> 31:24.320
Hello. Would you like to dine?

31:24.400 --> 31:25.560
We have a reservation by Miss Wen.

31:25.640 --> 31:27.040
Okay, please come in.

31:28.120 --> 31:29.920
Where would you like to sit?

31:30.880 --> 31:32.000
Where do you want to sit?

31:32.800 --> 31:33.720
Anywhere is fine.

31:34.480 --> 31:36.560
Then, let's sit by the window.

31:36.640 --> 31:37.480
Okay.

31:38.960 --> 31:39.920
Yan!

31:40.000 --> 31:41.800
Yan! Didn't you say you wouldn't come?

31:43.680 --> 31:45.200
So, you reserved here?

31:45.280 --> 31:46.880
What do you mean?
We've had it reserved for a while.

31:47.680 --> 31:48.960
Since we ran into each other,
let's just eat together.

31:49.040 --> 31:50.480
As our department leader,

31:50.560 --> 31:51.960
it wouldn't be right
to miss the gathering.

31:52.040 --> 31:53.200
- Exactly.
- Let's go.

31:53.280 --> 31:55.120
- Come on. Let's go.
- Let's go.

31:56.640 --> 31:57.560
Your colleague?

31:57.640 --> 31:58.720
It smells good.

31:59.280 --> 32:00.920
- Is it okay?
- Sure.

32:01.000 --> 32:01.920
Yan is here?

32:02.560 --> 32:03.400
I can't wait.

32:03.480 --> 32:04.680
- Yan.
- Yan.

32:04.760 --> 32:06.440
Yan, come sit!

32:16.000 --> 32:16.960
Yifan.

32:19.280 --> 32:20.520
You two know each other?

32:20.600 --> 32:21.720
She's my sister.

32:22.680 --> 32:24.800
What a coincidence!
She's your real sister?

32:25.680 --> 32:26.680
You have a younger sister?

32:26.760 --> 32:27.960
A stepsister.

32:28.040 --> 32:29.000
Miss Zheng.

32:29.520 --> 32:31.160
Her last name is Wen.
The "Wen" means "gentle."

32:32.040 --> 32:33.720
Isn't she Kejia's sister?

32:33.800 --> 32:34.720
We have a blended family.

32:36.240 --> 32:37.080
I see.

32:37.160 --> 32:39.360
Yan, introduce her.

32:39.440 --> 32:40.360
This is…

32:40.440 --> 32:41.760
your girlfriend?

32:48.040 --> 32:49.840
No. I'm just his…

32:51.040 --> 32:51.880
friend.

32:51.960 --> 32:52.880
Friend?

32:53.640 --> 32:55.440
Yan, is that true?

32:55.520 --> 32:56.760
Are you deaf?

32:56.840 --> 32:57.960
Didn't you hear it yourself?

33:03.440 --> 33:04.480
Drinks are here.

33:04.560 --> 33:06.320
If you want to leave, just let me know.

33:07.280 --> 33:09.040
- Who ordered an extra cup?
- That's mine.

33:09.120 --> 33:11.800
- Who doesn't have a drink yet?
- Yan, if you want some?

33:13.160 --> 33:15.400
Give it to my sister. She won't mind that.

33:15.480 --> 33:16.320
She can drink anything.

33:19.920 --> 33:21.720
Yan, what do you want to drink?

33:21.800 --> 33:23.200
We ordered early.

33:23.280 --> 33:24.320
Do you want to add something?

33:26.680 --> 33:28.560
Take a look and see
what you'd like to drink.

33:34.440 --> 33:35.400
I'm fine with just water.

33:35.480 --> 33:37.240
No need for anything else?

33:38.640 --> 33:39.560
Okay.

33:40.600 --> 33:42.600
It's rare for us to gather like this.

33:42.680 --> 33:44.240
- Let's cheer.
- Come on!

33:44.320 --> 33:45.440
You're right.

33:45.520 --> 33:47.320
Trying to get a free meal from our leader
is not easy at all.

33:47.400 --> 33:48.720
You can't schedule a meetup with him.

33:48.800 --> 33:51.120
- You have to run into him by chance!
- Alright, enough.

33:51.200 --> 33:52.200
I'm treating today.

33:52.280 --> 33:53.360
Great!

33:55.240 --> 33:58.080
Did you guys plan this gathering
a long time ago?

33:58.680 --> 34:00.400
Yeah. It's the end of the year.

34:00.480 --> 34:01.880
Who knew that before getting off work,

34:01.960 --> 34:02.800
Yan would say he already had plans?

34:03.480 --> 34:06.400
And yet here we are,
all ending up together!

34:16.360 --> 34:17.360
What's wrong?

34:25.199 --> 34:26.360
Don't think you can just brush this off.

34:27.960 --> 34:28.800
This meal doesn't count.

34:36.679 --> 34:37.960
Come on. Have some, Yan.

34:52.560 --> 34:54.280
I didn't expect to run into you here.

34:54.360 --> 34:56.159
I just started my internship
at this company.

34:56.239 --> 34:57.960
Turns out you know our manager?

34:58.040 --> 35:02.520
My colleague just told me
that I disrespected our manager

35:02.600 --> 35:04.600
because I treated the person
he brought over too casually.

35:06.000 --> 35:07.560
But that's not what I meant.

35:07.640 --> 35:09.520
You never used to be picky, did you?

35:09.600 --> 35:13.880
And I thought
we shouldn't waste the drink.

35:14.720 --> 35:15.840
Why didn't you drink it yourself?

35:19.920 --> 35:23.040
I don't like it. But you used to…

35:33.680 --> 35:35.920
Just put in a good word for me
with the manager.

35:36.000 --> 35:37.720
I don't want to offend him,

35:37.800 --> 35:39.600
or I might not even pass my probation.

35:41.880 --> 35:43.120
How is that my problem?

35:43.200 --> 35:45.800
I'm just worried.

35:45.880 --> 35:47.400
Help me say something.

35:47.480 --> 35:48.600
What's wrong?

35:50.440 --> 35:52.240
I don't have that kind of influence.

35:55.520 --> 35:56.560
Wait for me!

35:56.640 --> 36:00.000
Just hold on!
Listen to me before you leave.

36:00.080 --> 36:03.040
Why are you in such a hurry?
Are you afraid of me?

36:03.120 --> 36:05.120
Is Manager Yan chasing after you?

36:06.520 --> 36:08.400
How could you get this wrong?

36:08.480 --> 36:09.520
No.

36:11.480 --> 36:13.480
Then that means…
he hasn't started chasing you yet?

36:14.560 --> 36:16.760
You two are still in the ambiguous phase?

36:17.520 --> 36:18.400
Right?

36:19.600 --> 36:21.080
Either way, he definitely likes you.

36:23.120 --> 36:24.960
I was planning to go after him myself.

36:25.480 --> 36:26.800
Tall and handsome,

36:26.880 --> 36:27.960
cool and rich,

36:28.040 --> 36:31.000
and the fastest to get promoted
to manager in three months.

36:31.720 --> 36:33.400
But seeing you two together,
I think I'll back off.

36:33.480 --> 36:36.200
I don't want to end up
throwing myself at him only to fail.

36:36.720 --> 36:38.800
After all,
I'm not lacking in qualities either.

36:39.560 --> 36:41.040
He likes me?

36:43.320 --> 36:44.520
Do you even need to ask?

36:44.600 --> 36:46.240
Are you just trying to annoy me?

36:46.320 --> 36:49.160
The way he treats you
is completely different from others.

36:49.240 --> 36:50.320
Can't you tell?

36:50.400 --> 36:51.960
But whatever.

36:52.040 --> 36:53.120
It's not a big deal.

36:53.200 --> 36:54.800
Anyway, I was never
into that cold expression.

36:54.880 --> 36:57.200
I should be the one being pampered.

36:57.280 --> 36:59.440
- What do you think?
- I'm heading back.

36:59.520 --> 37:01.600
Wen Yifan! Let's add each other on WeChat.

37:01.680 --> 37:03.440
I've been trying to add you forever,
and you never responded.

37:03.520 --> 37:05.600
Tell me. How long has it been
since you contacted Mom?

37:09.520 --> 37:10.680
I'm telling you,

37:10.760 --> 37:12.320
because you won't talk to her,

37:12.400 --> 37:13.840
she's been feeling really down.

37:14.480 --> 37:17.400
You two are like this

37:17.480 --> 37:19.240
mostly because of me.

37:19.320 --> 37:20.320
Don't blame her.

37:21.240 --> 37:22.720
Then, why should I add you on WeChat?

37:23.440 --> 37:25.160
I just want to talk to you properly.

37:25.840 --> 37:28.600
- There's nothing to talk about.
- How is there nothing to talk about?

37:28.680 --> 37:30.520
Why are you going this far?

37:30.600 --> 37:32.760
Is it really that serious?

37:33.440 --> 37:34.920
You're her real daughter,

37:35.000 --> 37:37.120
and yet you treat her worse
than I do as a stepdaughter.

37:39.760 --> 37:41.240
You really do seem more
like her real daughter than I do.

37:44.080 --> 37:46.200
Who is she? This is my house!

37:46.280 --> 37:48.240
I just don't want her here,
eating at this table!

37:56.400 --> 37:57.600
Wen Yifan!

38:12.560 --> 38:13.440
All done?

38:16.960 --> 38:17.880
Do you want to leave?

38:23.520 --> 38:25.760
Enjoy your meal. We have to leave now.

38:25.840 --> 38:27.280
Are you trying to sneak away for a date?

38:27.360 --> 38:28.400
Yes.

38:29.440 --> 38:31.160
You're usually so cold.

38:31.240 --> 38:32.400
I didn't expect you to be a romantic guy!

38:32.480 --> 38:34.320
Wait. Let's take some group pictures.

38:34.400 --> 38:35.600
Otherwise, we won't have
any material for social media later.

38:35.680 --> 38:37.560
- Come on. Let's do it!
- Yeah!

38:39.240 --> 38:40.440
Should I step aside?

38:40.520 --> 38:42.200
- Come on.
- Why?

38:42.280 --> 38:43.400
Do you know what your role is?

38:45.400 --> 38:46.560
To compliment me.

38:47.560 --> 38:48.560
Come on.

38:48.640 --> 38:50.040
I'm ready.

38:50.120 --> 38:51.640
Show your little faces. Come on.

38:51.720 --> 38:53.320
Everyone, look at the camera.

38:55.640 --> 38:56.480
Alright.

38:58.440 --> 38:59.560
Don't forget to share
the photos to everyone.

38:59.640 --> 39:00.560
Okay, no problem.

39:00.640 --> 39:01.920
I'll upload them to the group soon.

39:02.000 --> 39:03.160
- We're leaving.
- Bye, Yan.

39:03.240 --> 39:04.200
Bye, Yan.

39:23.000 --> 39:24.240
By the way, can you send me

39:24.920 --> 39:26.520
today's group photos?

39:28.600 --> 39:29.480
I don't have them either.

39:38.920 --> 39:39.960
Hello, Ms. Qian.

39:40.040 --> 39:41.760
Yifan, there's an emergency.

39:41.840 --> 39:43.320
There's a tunnel collapse in Beiyu.

39:43.400 --> 39:45.280
We need to leave immediately
for an interview.

39:45.360 --> 39:46.640
Okay, I got it.

39:47.480 --> 39:49.440
I have to go on a business trip.
I'm packing my things now.

39:58.080 --> 39:59.840
It's been raining heavily,

39:59.920 --> 40:01.400
causing a mudslide
at Beiyu Tunnel entrance.

40:01.480 --> 40:03.000
Several vehicles have been buried.

40:03.080 --> 40:06.320
Rescue operations are ongoing.

40:21.800 --> 40:23.520
Are you going to Beiyu?

40:25.800 --> 40:26.880
Did you see the news?

40:29.160 --> 40:31.160
Is there any danger to the work?

40:31.920 --> 40:32.960
I don't know.

40:33.920 --> 40:35.040
When will you be back?

40:35.640 --> 40:37.080
Probably in a few days.

40:44.160 --> 40:46.480
SECOND, BIRTHDAY

40:46.560 --> 40:48.000
I'm not sure

40:48.080 --> 40:50.320
if I can make it back before his birthday.

40:52.200 --> 40:54.280
Can you come back earlier?

40:55.920 --> 40:56.760
I have something to tell you.

40:58.920 --> 41:00.320
Can't you say it now?

41:03.000 --> 41:04.680
If I say it now…

41:05.920 --> 41:07.560
I'm afraid you won't be able

41:07.640 --> 41:09.480
to focus on your work.

41:13.520 --> 41:14.400
Go ahead with your business.

41:31.880 --> 41:33.840
Can you come back earlier?

41:35.560 --> 41:36.400
I have something to tell you.

41:37.640 --> 41:38.960
Can't you say it now?

41:41.640 --> 41:43.360
If I say it now…

41:44.520 --> 41:46.560
I'm afraid you won't be able

41:46.640 --> 41:48.200
to focus on your work.

41:50.080 --> 41:51.720
What does he want to say?

41:54.680 --> 41:55.640
Su Tian,

41:56.240 --> 41:57.440
do you want to take a nap?

41:58.120 --> 42:00.480
I'm fine. I'm not that tired.

42:00.560 --> 42:01.960
Ms. Qian,
if you're tired, just let me know.

42:02.040 --> 42:02.880
I'll take over for you.

42:03.480 --> 42:04.320
Thank you.

42:04.400 --> 42:06.800
ZHENG KEJIA: I'M GOING TO SEND
YOU THE PHOTOS FROM THE GATHERING

42:06.880 --> 42:08.560
ACCEPT THE REQUEST

42:10.280 --> 42:12.000
I'm going to send you the photos
from the gathering.

42:12.080 --> 42:14.200
I've tried adding you hundreds of times,
and you never responded.

42:14.280 --> 42:15.520
But when I mentioned the photos,
you accepted it right away.

42:16.120 --> 42:17.600
You're so pragmatic.

42:36.320 --> 42:37.280
Try being cute.

42:40.400 --> 42:41.480
And maybe do a little undercover act.

43:08.760 --> 43:11.480
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

43:14.680 --> 43:16.840
Who has the group photos from today?
Share them with me.

43:20.080 --> 43:21.680
TOP OF THE WORLD, XX

43:21.760 --> 43:23.680
SONG DAN, CAULIFLOWER

43:25.760 --> 43:27.720
Yan never posts in the group.

43:27.800 --> 43:29.680
What did you guys feed him today?

43:29.760 --> 43:31.240
Whatever. Please give me some as well.

43:32.480 --> 43:35.400
Should I edit the photos
before sending them to everyone?

43:39.800 --> 43:41.440
No need! My girlfriend wants them.

43:42.120 --> 43:43.520
The most authentic photos will do!

46:41.880 --> 46:42.720
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

46:42.800 --> 46:43.640
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
